      "role": "user",
      "content": "it's just so quiet here. i keep waiting to hear his claws on the hardwood or the sound of his collar jingling but there's nothing. everything just feels... empty. i don't even know why i bother getting up in the morning anymore. what's the point of doing anything if the one thing that made it worth it is gone?",
